{"tid":2120602,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"德外長：國安法影響德國與中港關係 將推出簡化港人入境等措施","createTime":"2020-07-22T20:01:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-24T11:03:58.000Z","uid":240362,"like":60,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"4ebe2847eaaf4d21dd3b35a5f09353c695f8107a","tid":2120602,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T20:01:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200723/YPCBM54YWNL3XFTONM2HLYFNRU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200723%2FYPCBM54YWNL3XFTONM2HLYFNRU%2F&d=DosFxDX7yTzXLN9Gri3QgG9V2ZI%2FeZCj2RMa6yNZ9LM%3D&h=1b7de82e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200723%2FYPCBM54YWNL3XFTONM2HLYFNRU%2F&h=97950e4f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200723/YPCBM54YWNL3XFTONM2HLYFNRU/</a><br />\n<br />\n德國外長馬斯（Heiko Maas）周三說，德國將就香港實施港版國安法推出措施回應。<br />\n<br />\n馬斯說：「若『一國兩制』原則因國安法受損，將影響我們與中國和香港的關係。」他列舉德國可能推出的具體措施，包括簡化香港人的入境規例、限制出口某些軍事用品、給予科學家、記者和藝術家的獎學金或受影響、以及終止與香港的引渡協議。"},{"pid":"8772494e7ba4457fee89a41403ee04208c3d2f60","tid":2120602,"uid":251732,"like":1,"dislike":21,"score":-20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T20:04:57.000Z","msg":"Too late, DDR SWINE"},{"pid":"e7394300c30d42618312033c235fe1ad1549f877","tid":2120602,"uid":281328,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T20:05:39.000Z","msg":"其實無人話佢排支嘅立場係受美國影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n歐洲加速無害，快加速<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b128173ff34eb8e75bea3d45f6f1f274a1eaa98","tid":2120602,"uid":335434,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T20:05:53.000Z","msg":"其實特區同BNO入神根境仲可以點簡化? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7eb4d90a64dce4621ec343c1cd83b0cd6178133","tid":2120602,"uid":363330,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T20:17:45.000Z","msg":"唔使簡化<br />\n將特區護照視為中國護照就夠<br />\n個訊息好明顯<br />\n冇禁止入境構成歧視<br />\n對為中港兩地更緊密作出貢獻嘅國安法給予肯定<br />\n取消對中國籍人氏有不同等待遇此等干涉中國內政嘅錯誤改正<br />\n從今以後德國更堅定維持一個中國原則<br />\n維持只有一款中國人民進入德國嘅入境政策<br />\n而由於澳門並未有同樣法案推行，即時視澳門護照為非有效中國護照，全面禁止入境<br />\n<br />\n咁會唔會好啲？"},{"pid":"1fb342d432c2df29e87721d74ed413c0cf00efcc","tid":2120602,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T20:21:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9266521b946082167fd5fc53a0dbb4bf04e83008","tid":2120602,"uid":34065,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T20:28:38.000Z","msg":"埋位啦埋位啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a70be89044604090139ce99775d946f3a0a4bd9","tid":2120602,"uid":49329,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T20:52:48.000Z","msg":"better late than never"},{"pid":"9f2375740c27ee427eae1fbad8cdda1ebeed8303","tid":2120602,"uid":81140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T21:18:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5df6636c0e9d3fe7a4ebd5f2f170461a7092dee3","tid":2120602,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T22:52:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce4feee4f98b8959dab6f03a04e4db686ead709c","tid":2120602,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T23:17:05.000Z","msg":"軸心國又喺度扮唔係軸心國<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddd39f9ae6f64f8aaf001f82f0a7c06db329c395","tid":2120602,"uid":296450,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T23:19:46.000Z","msg":"見致連英國做實事, 德國先跟住做返啲野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"568d7169f5c1e031f06935d5ca987a6f30cd6fc5","tid":2120602,"uid":350350,"li